<paragraph blockId="22.[151,887,930,990]" box="[151,887,930,956]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,887,930,956]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,887,930,956]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<taxonomicName authority="Cope, 1862" authorityName="Cope" authorityYear="1862" box="[151,508,930,956]" class="Reptilia" family="Boidae" genus="Epicrates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="crassus">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,362,930,956]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Epicrates crassus</emphasis>
Cope, 
<number box="[449,508,930,956]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="1862.0">1862</number>
</taxonomicName>
“Salamanta, Cobra-arco-íris”
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[151,887,930,990]" box="[151,370,965,990]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">(Figs. 9.5 and 22.2)</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1436,1037,1278]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
Recorded only in northern Minas Gerais, municipalities of Manga and Mato Verde, 
<number box="[1118,1160,1038,1062]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="440.0">440</number>
and 
<quantity box="[1218,1292,1037,1062]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.41" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" unit="m" value="541.0">541 m</quantity>
of elevation respectively. These records are located next to the Cerrado contact area, and the vegetation of this area is bushy and arboreal caatinga in contact with cerrado savannas. This species is considered a Cerrado endemic species (
<bibRefCitation author="Nogueira" box="[158,401,1145,1170]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refString="Nogueira, C., Colli, G. R., Costa, G. &amp; Machado, R. B. (2010) Diversidade de repteis Squamata e evolucao do conhecimento faunistico no Cerrado. In: Diniz, I. R., Marinho-Filho, J., Machado, R. B. &amp; Cavalcanti, R. B. (Eds.), Cerrado: conhecimento cientifico quantitativo como subsidio para acoes de conservacao. Editora UNB, Brasilia, pp. 333 - 375." type="book chapter" year="2010">
Nogueira 
<emphasis box="[274,333,1145,1170]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[342,401,1146,1170]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2010.2011">2010</number>
</bibRefCitation>
, 2011), with wide distribution in central Brazilian open areas (
<bibRefCitation author="Passos" box="[1129,1432,1145,1170]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refString="Passos, P. &amp; Fernandes, R. (2008) Revision of the Epicrates cenchria complex (Serpentes: Boidae). Herpetological Monographs, 22, 1 - 30. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1655 / 06 - 003.1" type="journal article" year="2008">
Passos &amp; Fernandes 
<number box="[1372,1432,1146,1170]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2008.0">2008</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Recoder" box="[151,382,1181,1206]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refString="Recoder, R., Teixeira Junior, M., Camacho, A., Nunes, P. M. S., Mott, T., Valdujo, P. H., Guellere, J. M. &amp; Rodrigues, M. T. (2011) Repteis da Estacao Ecologica Serra Geral do Tocantins, Brasil Central. Biota Neotropica, 11, 263 - 282. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1590 / S 1676 - 06032011000100026" type="journal article" year="2011">
Recoder 
<emphasis box="[254,313,1181,1206]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[322,382,1182,1206]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2011.0">2011</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). We do not exclude possible future records for other localities along the Caatinga-Cerrado contact zone, in the states of Bahia, Piauí, and Maranhão. It has semi-arboreal habits, is nocturnal, and feeds on vertebrates (
<bibRefCitation author="Marques" box="[288,519,1253,1278]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refString="Marques, O. A. V., Eterovic, A., Strussmann, C. &amp; Sazima, I. (2005) Serpentes do Pantanal: Guia ilustrado. Holos Editora, Ribeirao Preto, 184 pp." type="book" year="2005">
Marques 
<emphasis box="[395,444,1253,1278]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">et al</emphasis>
. 
<number box="[458,519,1253,1278]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2005.0">2005</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
